      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0003",
      "text": "LS_ACC: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        142.05,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0004",
      "text": "LS_ACC signifies that the destination Nx_Port reinstated the Recovery_Qualifier.  The for-",
      "bbox": [
        142.08,
        57.65,
        540.06,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0005",
      "text": "mat of the LS_ACC Payload is shown in table 22.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        314.26,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0006",
      "text": "4.2.13",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.97,
        123.76,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0007",
      "text": "Request Sequence Initiative (RSI)",
      "bbox": [
        133.76,
        178.97,
        292.65,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0008",
      "text": "4.2.13.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        192.63,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0009",
      "text": "The RSI ELS is used to request that Sequence Initiative be passed to the Sequence Recipient of an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        540.08,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0010",
      "text": "Exchange in progress.  A request to pass Sequence Initiative shall only be accepted if the Originator",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.05,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0011",
      "text": "Nx_Port or the Responder Nx_Port of the target Exchange makes the request.  A separate Exchange",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        540.04,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0012",
      "text": "shall be used to perform the Request Sequence Initiative.  The Payload shall contain the OX_ID and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.08,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0013",
      "text": "RX_ID for the target Exchange, in addition to the S_ID of the Nx_Port that originated the Exchange.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        540.05,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0014",
      "text": "The LS_ACC Reply is sent subsequent to the transfer of Sequence Initiative on the target Exchange.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        540.03,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0015",
      "text": "Transmission of RSI is allowed while the identified Exchange is open.  Both the Originator and Re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        540.11,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0016",
      "text": "sponder shall ensure that the OX_ID and RX_ID pair for which Sequence Initiative is being passed",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        539.92,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0017",
      "text": "are currently associated with the OX_ID and RX_ID pair specified in the RSI Request.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        474.8,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0018",
      "text": "If there is a Sequence active for the target Exchange, the Sequence Initiator of the active Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        539.97,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0019",
      "text": "of the target Exchange shall terminate them and transfer Sequence Initiative as follows:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        482.09,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0020",
      "text": "a) If there is an active Sequence for which the last Data frame has not been transmitted, the Se-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        394.96,
        540.06,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0021",
      "text": "quence Initiator of the target Exchange shall terminate the Sequence by transmitting a Data",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        406.96,
        539.85,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0022",
      "text": "frame with the End_Sequence and Sequence Initiative bits set to one in F_CTL.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        418.96,
        474.68,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0023",
      "text": "b) If there are no Data frames to be sent for the active Sequence, the Sequence Initiator of the tar-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        442.96,
        540.12,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0024",
      "text": "get Exchange shall transmit a NOP Basic Link Service frame (see FC-FS-2) with the",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        454.96,
        539.93,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0025",
      "text": "End_Sequence and Sequence Initiative bits set to one in F_CTL.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        466.96,
        409.15,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0026",
      "text": "If there is no Sequence active, the Sequence Initiator of the target Exchange shall transfer Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        539.91,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0027",
      "text": "Initiative by initiating a new Sequence consisting of a single NOP Basic Link Service frame (a one",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        539.9,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0028",
      "text": "frame Sequence) with the End_Sequence and Sequence Initiative bits set to 1 in F_CTL.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        488.34,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0029",
      "text": "The LS_ACC to the Exchange requesting Sequence Initiative shall be transmitted after Sequence Ini-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        540.07,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p057_s0030",
      "text": "tiative has been passed (see FC-FS-2) on the target Exchange.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        376.57,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
